71
00:05:09,683 --> 00:05:11,283
And the other?

72
00:05:11,283 --> 00:05:12,683
Yes.

73
00:05:12,683 --> 00:05:16,683
In his coat pocket, we found this black necktie.

74
00:05:18,483 --> 00:05:20,483
Could this be the murder weapon?

