00:09:18,783 --> 00:09:20,283
Yes, sir!

161
00:09:21,883 --> 00:09:23,883
-Yuko. -Yeah?

162
00:09:23,883 --> 00:09:28,283
May I speak to you in the living room for a moment?

163
00:09:28,283 --> 00:09:30,083
Sure.

164
00:09:33,483 --> 00:09:37,083
So? What's it about?

165
00:09:37,083 --> 00:09:40,083
Article 42, sub-paragraph 01 of the penal code...

166
00:09:40,083 --> 00:09:41,083
What?

167
00:09:41,083 --> 00:09:42,483
Criminal offenders who turn themselves in

168
00:09:42,483 --> 00:09:46,083
before authorities discover anything

169
00:09:46,083 --> 00:09:49,983
